le=\"Melissa Blackwood\">Melissa Blackwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Tarbeck\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ellyn Tarbeck\">Ellyn Tarbeck</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Merrell\" title=\"Harry Merrell\">Harry Merrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harsley\" title=\"Harsley\">Harsley</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ormond_(knight)\" title=\"Ormond (knight)\">Ormond</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lacey\" title=\"Lacey\">Lacey</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_48&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Brienne was last seen in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>; Sansa, in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 41\">Chapter 41</a>; and Sandor, in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_74\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 74\">Chapter 74</a>. Brienne's story is almost certainly false, given the last known situations of all three characters.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_48&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.tor.com/2015/07/09/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-dance-with-dragons-part-28/\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Dance with Dragons, Part 28</a> Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115729\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.223 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 275/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1300/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8767/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1756/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 568/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  204.495      1 -total\n 98.19%  200.792      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ADwD\n 97.76%  199.921      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 97.38%  199.134      1 Template:Infobox\n  1.00%    2.040      1 Template:Notes\n  0.76%    1.546      1 Template:References\n  0.56%    1.142      2 Template:Work_color\n  0.37%    0.764      1 Template:Columns\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westero